          "path": "05-marketing/video-script-15s.md",
          "content": "# Tallow Native — 15-Second Social Media Ad Script\n\n**Version:** 1.0  \n**Format:** Social media ad (Instagram Reels, TikTok, YouTube Shorts)  \n**Tone:** Fast, visual, punchy — but not hype\n\n---\n\n## VERSION A — \"The Problem / Solution\"\n\n**[0:00–0:03]**  \n**[SHOT: Wide shot of person holding heavy cast iron pot with oven mitts, clearly struggling with hot fat. Text overlay: \"🤕 Every time.\"]**  \n**No VO**\n\n**[0:03–0:08]**  \n**[CUT TO: Close-up of T-handle wrench lowering through hot fat. One turn. Tallow draining clean into catcher below.]**  \n**VO (voiceover):** \"Or — drain it through the bottom of the pot.\"\n\n**[0:08–0:12]**  \n**[CUT TO: Solid tallow puck dropping into pot. Clean. Satisfying.]**  \n**VO:** \"Filter it. Store it. Drop it back in for the next batch.\"\n\n**[0:12–0:15]**  \n**[Logo on cream: TALLOW NATIVE + tallownative.com]**  \n**VO:** \"Tallow Native. Built for the fryer.\"\n\n---\n\n## VERSION B — \"The Puck Drop\" (visual-first, for muted scroll)\n\n**[0:00–0:06]**  \n**[SHOT: Inverted tallow catcher over pot. Vent button pressed. Solid tallow puck drops into pot in one smooth motion. Macro shot. Subtitles: \"Solid tallow puck. Drops clean. Every time.\"]**\n\n**[0:06–0:11]**  \n**[CUT TO: Product shot — pot + catcher + wrench. Subtitle: \"M18×1.5 drain port. Mirror-polished SS catcher. Zero plastic.\"]**\n\n**[0:11–0:15]**  \n**[Logo on navy: TALLOW NATIVE + \"Built for the fryer\" + tallownative.com]**  \n**Subtitle: \"Reserve yours — first run ships [DATE]\"**\n\n---\n\n## VERSION C — \"The Engineering Hook\"\n\n**[0:00–0:04]**  \n**[SHOT: Extreme close-up of M18×1.5 thread in cast iron. Text: \"This is an automotive oil drain plug thread.\"]**\n\n**[0:04–0:10]**  \n**[CUT TO: Same thread spec in pot bottom. VO: \"We put one in a Dutch oven.\"]**  \n**[SHOT: Tallow draining through the port. Clean. Precise.]**\n\n**[0:10–0:15]**  \n**[Logo + URL]**  \n**VO: \"Tallow Native. The Dutch oven with a drain.\"**\n\n---\n\n## PRODUCTION NOTES FOR 15-SECOND ADS\n\n- **First 3 seconds are everything.** The scroll stops or it doesn't.\n- **Assume muted.** All key information must be readable as text overlays.\n- **Show the puck drop.** It's the most immediately understandable image of what makes the product different. Use it in at least one version.\n- **No announcer voice.** Use real VO if you use VO at all — or go text-only.\n- **Aspect ratio:** 9:16 for Stories/Reels/Shorts; 1:1 optional for feed ads\n- **End card:** Always include URL + product name. 3 seconds minimum.\n- **CTA text options for button:**  \n  - \"Reserve yours\"  \n  - \"Shop now\"  \n  - \"Learn more\"  \n  - \"First run — limited\"\n"
