          "content": "# Tallow Native — Complete Packaging Copy\n\n---\n\n## INNER BOX — EXTERIOR\n\n### Side A (Front):\nTALLOW NATIVE\n\nThe Dutch Oven System\n\nBuilt for the fryer.\n\n---\n\n### Side B (Back):\n**THE TALLOW NATIVE DUTCH OVEN SYSTEM**\n\nYou've put real money into your tallow. You deserve a system that treats it accordingly.\n\nThe Tallow Native Dutch Oven System is a three-piece cast iron and stainless steel cooking system designed for home cooks who fry in beef tallow, lard, duck fat, and other animal fats worth keeping.\n\nThe Dutch oven drains from the bottom. A precision M18×1.5 threaded drain port — modeled on the automotive oil drain plug system — lets you drain hot tallow through the pot floor, into the stainless catcher below, using the included 12-inch T-handle wrench. No tilting. No pouring. No burns.\n\nThe catcher filters your fat through 150-micron stainless wire mesh, stores it sealed in the refrigerator, and releases it as a clean solid puck when you're ready for the next batch.\n\nZero plastic anywhere. Enameled cast iron. 304 stainless steel. Copper crush washers. Food-grade silicone.\n\ntallownative.com\n\n---\n\n**CONTAINS:**\n\n01 — Dutch oven body (5.5 qt enameled cast iron, M18×1.5 drain port, drain plug installed)  \n01 — Dutch oven lid (enameled cast iron, silicone gasket, vent plug installed)  \n01 — Tallow catcher (304 SS, mirror electropolished, filter installed, vent button installed)  \n01 — Storage lid for catcher (304 SS, silicone-sealed)  \n01 — T-handle hex wrench (12\", 14mm AF, 304 SS)  \n05 — Spare copper crush washers (M18, copper C110)  \n01 — 2-piece cheesecloth ring adapter (304 SS)  \n01 — Quick-start guide  \n01 — Full product manual  \n01 — Recipe card  \n\n---\n\n**CARE:**\n- Interior enamel: Hand wash or dishwasher safe\n- Stainless catcher: Dishwasher safe; hand wash to maintain mirror polish\n- Drain plug: Remove and replace crush washer after each plug removal\n- Do not heat pot empty above 500°F (260°C)\n- Do not add cold water to hot pot (thermal shock risk)\n\n**COOKTOP COMPATIBILITY:** Gas ✓ Electric ✓ Induction ✓ Ceramic ✓\n\n---\n\n**LEGAL / COMPLIANCE:**\n\nEnameled surfaces: Lead and cadmium free. Complies with FDA 21 CFR 175.300. California Prop 65 compliant. 304 Stainless steel certified AISI 304. Silicone: FDA 21 CFR 177.2600. Manufactured to food contact material standards.\n\n**WARNING:** Contains heavy cast iron components. Use caution when lifting. Surfaces become hot during use — always use heat-protective gloves or oven mitts when handling. Do not leave unattended on open flame. Keep out of reach of children during use.\n\nTALLOW NATIVE LLC | [City], Texas | tallownative.com  \nMade with care from enameled cast iron and 304 stainless steel.  \nBatch: [BATCH CODE] | MFD: [DATE]\n\nUPC: [BARCODE]\n\n---\n\n### Side C (Left side):\nRENDER.\nFILTER.\nREST.\nREPEAT.\n\n---\n\n### Side D (Right side):\n[System diagram — line art]\nThe complete fat lifecycle.\n\n---\n\n## INNER BOX — INTERIOR LID\n\nWHAT'S IN THE BOX\n\n01  Dutch oven (5.5 qt enameled cast iron)\n    drain plug and crush washer installed\n\n02  Dutch oven lid (enameled cast iron)\n    silicone gasket and vent plug installed\n\n03  Tallow catcher (304 stainless steel)\n    filter disc, vent button, and storage lid installed\n\n04  T-handle hex wrench (304 SS, 12\", 14mm AF)\n\n05  Accessory bag: 5 spare copper crush washers\n    and 2-piece cheesecloth ring adapter\n\n06  Quick-start guide · Full manual · Recipe card\n\n────────────────────────────────────────\nQuestions? support@tallownative.com\ntallownative.com | Built for the fryer.\n\n---\n\n## OUTER SHIPPING BOX\n\n**Top face:**\nTALLOW NATIVE\nDutch Oven System\ntallownative.com\n\n**Long side face:**\nBuilt for the fryer.\nHandle with care — heavy cast iron\ntallownative.com\n\n**Shipping label area:** [Preprinted label area, standard dimensions]\n\n**Fragile stamp:** FRAGILE — Enameled Cast Iron\n\n**Orientation arrow:** THIS SIDE UP ↑\n\n---\n\n## ACCESSORY BAG\n\n[Tallow Native badge logo, screen printed]\n\n**On tag attached to bag drawstring:**\n\nACCESSORY KIT\n\nContents:\n5 × Spare copper crush washers (M18 spec)\n1 × Cheesecloth ring adapter (2 pieces, 304 SS)\n\nReplace crush washer after each drain plug removal.\nReplacement washers: M18 × 24mm OD × 2mm copper, automotive spec.\n\ntallownative.com\n\n---\n\n## TISSUE PAPER\n\n\"TALLOW NATIVE\" repeated in light pattern (optional print)\n\n---\n\n*End of Packaging Copy — Version 1.0*\n"
